38,0.01987595,0.06317227,-0.02039953,-0.02308037,0.05321009,0.21269326,0.03460858,0.00264987,-0.00087573,-0.01278414,0.03822767,0.11692224,0.02401815,-0.045434,-0.00427263,0.07998358,-0.00394013,0.02264616,0.03903458,-0.01261712,0.02642282,0.0774051,-0.03379094,0.03946552,-0.01142349,-0.06146846,0.03441164,0.08630825,0.02042398,0.00688407,-0.0610012,0.01846963,0.01913502,-0.04294762,-0.01268894,0.00151121,-0.00326601,0.02136361,0.03421218,-0.00788325,-0.02031593,0.00327283,-0.02793418,0.00470626,-0.0151555,0.01129832,0.07466508,0.03208314],"last_embed":{"hash":"110kyre","tokens":441}}},"last_read":{"hash":"110kyre","at":1769676346554},"class_name":"SmartSource","last_import":{"mtime":1768980884000,"size":26265,"at":1769676327026,"hash":"110kyre"},"blocks":{"#":[1,375],"##{1}":[3,5],"##{2}":[6,7],"##{3}":[8,15],"##{4}":[16,18],"##{5}":[19,47],"##{6}":[48,170],"##{7}":[171,208],"##{8}":[209,330],"##{9}":[331,343],"##{10}":[344,357],"##{11}":[358,358],"##{12}":[359,367],"##{13}":[368,369],"##{14}":[370,375]},"outlinks":[{"title":"换元","target":"换元.md","line":9},{"title":"绝对值","target":"绝对值.md","line":10},{"title":"证明","target":"证明.md","line":11},{"title":"函数","target":"函数.md","line":12},{"title":"分段函数","target":"分段函数.md","line":13},{"title":"蛛网迭代","target":"蛛网迭代.md","line":14},{"title":"反函数","target":"反函数.md","line":15},{"title":"2,+\\infty)$, 这时, $y=x^2-5$ 的值域是 $[-1,+\\infty)$, 它没有超过 $D_y=[-1,+\\infty)$的范围, 这就是说复合函数 $z=f(g(x))$ 的定义域只能由 $y=g(x)$ 的定义域中^^^那些使 ^^^$g(x)$^^^ 属于 ^^^$z=f(y)$^^^ 的定义域的 ^^^$x$^^^ 组成^^^.\n    - \n    - \n    - 复合函数是由两个或多个函数经过\"[对应法则","target":"对应法则.md","line":22},{"title":"传递","target":"传递.md","line":25},{"title":"定义域","target":"定义域.md","line":26},{"title":"中间变量","target":"中间变量.md","line":31},{"title":"解析式(函数)","target":"解析式(函数","line":71},{"title":"值域","target":"值域.md","line":86},{"title":"换元","target":"换元.md","line":87},{"title":"幂函数","target":"chengbai高中数学框架(承白","line":115},{"title":"整数","target":"整数.md","line":173},{"title":"-8,+\\infty)$ 。\n        - 故答案为: $[-8,+\\infty)$.\n    - > 已知函数 $f(x)=\\log _2\\left(4^x+1\\right)-x+\\sqrt{x^2-1}$, 则关于 $x$ 的不等式 $f(x+2)>f(2 x)$解集为（）\n        - A. $\\left(-\\frac{2}{3}, 2\\right)$\n        - B. $-1, \\left.-\\frac{2}{3} \\cup \\right\\rvert\\, \\frac{1}{2}, 2$\n        - C. $-\\frac{2}{3},-\\frac{1}{2} \\cup \\frac{1}{2}, 2$\n        - D. $-1,-\\frac{1}{2} \\cup \\frac{1}{2}, 2$\n    - > 已知函数 $f(x)=2^x+\\frac{a}{2^2}$, 其中 $a$ 为实常数, 若 $f(0)=7$, 解关于 $x$ 的方程 $f(x)=5$;\n    - > 已知函数 $f(x)=2^x+m \\cdot 2^{-x}$ 的圏象关于原点对称。\n        - > (1) 判断函数 $f(x)$ 在定义域上的单调性, 并用单调性的定义证明;\n        - > (2) 设函数 $g(x)=\\log _a\\left[4^x+4^{-\\mathrm{x}}+2-a f(x)\\right","target":"a>0$ 且 $a \\neq 1","line":198},{"title":"单调性","target":"单调性.md","line":209},{"title":"函数性质","target":"函数性质.md","line":211},{"title":"单调性","target":"单调性.md","line":212},{"title":"2,+\\infty)$.\n    - > 已知 $f(x)=8+2 x-x^2$, 若 $g(x)=f\\left(2-x^2\\right)$, 则 g(x)\n        - A. 在区间 $(-1,0)$ 内是减函数\n        - B. 在区间 $(0,1)$ 内是减雨数\n        - C. 在区间 $(-2,0)$ 内是増畄数\n        - D. 在区间 $(0,2)$ 内是增通数\n    - > 函数 $f(x)=\\log _2\\left(1-x^2\\right)$ 的定义域为 $\\qquad$\n        - \n\n          $$(-1,1)$$\n\n          \n    - > 已知函数 $f(x)=\\log _2 \\cos \\left(2 x-\\frac{\\pi}{6}\\right)$ 的单调增区间为 $\\qquad$ .\n        - \n\n          $$\\left(k \\pi-\\frac{\\pi}{6}, k \\pi+\\frac{\\pi}{12}\\right), k \\in \\mathrm{Z}$$\n\n          \n    - \n    - \n    - \n    - \n    - #### [含参","target":"含参.md","line":254},{"title":"含参","target":"含参.md","line":326},{"title":"复合函数","target":"复合函数.md","line":327},{"title":"奇偶","target":"奇偶.md","line":331},{"title":"~来源~相似题~其他解法   ","target":"1题目/~来源~相似题~其他解法.md","line":339},{"title":"二级知识点","target":"1题目/二级知识点.md","line":340},{"title":"~总结 ","target":"1题目/~总结.md","line":341},{"title":"~答案","target":"1题目/~答案.md","line":342},{"title":"复合函数","target":"复合函数.md","line":345},{"title":"恒成立","target":"恒成立.md","line":359},{"title":"有解","target":"有解.md","line":359},{"title":"线性组合","target":"线性组合.md","line":368